# Call Detail Modal

## Trigger
- Opens when dispatcher clicks a call block
- Opens when clicking a pending call card

## Information Displayed

### Caller Info
- Caller name
- Callback number

### Pickup Info
- Location
- Department
- Room
- Pickup time
- Appointment duration

### Dropoff Info
- Location
- Department
- Room

### Patient Info
- First name
- Last name
- Date of birth
- Address
- Condition

### Insurance Info
- Primary insurance
- Policy number
- Authorization number
- Secondary insurance
- Tertiary insurance

### Notes
- Shared editable notes
- Visible to all dispatchers

## Behavior
- Clean layout
- Scrollable if needed
- Editable fields (future feature)